  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"ddb\">\n<p>A flurry of magic snowballs erupts from a point you choose within range. Each creature in a 5-foot-radius &amp;Reference[sphere]{sphere} centered on that point must make a &amp;Reference[dex]{Dexterity} saving throw. A creature takes 3d6 &amp;Reference[cold]{cold} damage on a failed save, or half as much damage on a successful one.</p>\n<p class=\"s19\"><strong>At Higher Levels.</strong> <span class=\"p\">When you cast this spell using a spell slot of 3rd level or higher, the damage increases by 1d6 for each slot level above 2nd.</span></p>\n</div>",
